TrenchBroom is a modern cross-platform level editor for Quake-engine based games.

=============================

This repository provides the Snap packaging basis for development, self-education
and advancement of existing software functionality on Snap-based systems.

Upstream website:
http://kristianduske.com/trenchbroom/

More information about Snap packages:
http://snapcraft.io/

Snap release builds:
https://code.launchpad.net/~beidl/trenchbroom/+git/trenchbroom
